### 5) README.md Review and Modernization

**Goal:** README becomes the fastest path from "clone" to "working app".

Location: `/README.md` (root)

Checklist:
- [ ] Clear one-paragraph value proposition
- [ ] Prerequisites match reality (Node 20+, pnpm 9+, Docker)
- [ ] Quickstart with minimal steps (copy/paste friendly)
- [ ] Environment variables section references `.env.shared` files
- [ ] Scripts section matches actual CLI commands
- [ ] Architecture overview links to docs for details
- [ ] "What's Running Locally?" table is accurate
- [ ] Troubleshooting for top recurring issues
- [ ] License and contribution info

Hard rule: do not claim support for providers/services unless it exists in code.

---

### 6) Verification (Cross-Check Everything)

Run the following:

```bash
# Lint docs
pnpm nx run docs:lint

# Build docs
pnpm nx run docs:build

# Start docs dev server
pnpm saas docs up

# Optional: Full build
pnpm nx run-many --target=build --projects=docs

# Optional: Type-check webapp (if you touched webapp code)
pnpm tsc --noEmit -p packages/webapp/tsconfig.app.json
```

If anything fails, fix the smallest root cause and re-run.

